    "F. Yahboom Mobile Robot Evaluation 1) Experimental Configuration: Test environment included:• Mixed criticality objects (fragile glassware, hot items).• Dynamic obstacles (moving humans, carts).• Real-time EKG updates from 8 wall-mounted cameras.",
